<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Terminal on NavyD的个人博客</title><link>/tags/terminal/</link><description>Recent content in Terminal on NavyD的个人博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Mar 2023 19:02:41 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="/tags/terminal/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Powerline in WSL2</title><link>/posts/2021/10/powerline-in-wsl2/</link><pubDate>Sun, 17 Oct 2021 16:19:48 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/2021/10/powerline-in-wsl2/</guid><description>&lt;img src="/posts/2021/10/powerline-in-wsl2/2021-10-17-20-09-02.png" alt="Featured image of post Powerline in WSL2" />&lt;p>在wsl2中使用zsh主题出现乱码时需要安装powerline字体才能显示，windows terminal使用的Cascadia Code字体也支持powerline版本
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/microsoft/cascadia-code#installation"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Cascadia Code&lt;/a>
，常用的还有
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/powerline/fonts"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>powerline/fonts&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;p>对于Cascadia Code字体下载
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/microsoft/cascadia-code/releases"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>microsoft/cascadia-code/releases&lt;/a>
解压安装即可：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="/posts/2021/10/powerline-in-wsl2/2021-10-17-20-09-02.png"
width="836"
height="385"
srcset="/posts/2021/10/powerline-in-wsl2/2021-10-17-20-09-02_hu_4005b900ffdf5d0b.png 480w, /posts/2021/10/powerline-in-wsl2/2021-10-17-20-09-02_hu_c0c55995f2f387dc.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="217"
data-flex-basis="521px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>对于powerline字体文件可以使用&lt;code>git clone https://github.com/powerline/fonts.git --depth=1&lt;/code>下载后在管理员权限下执行安装
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/powerline/fonts/blob/master/install.ps1"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>install.ps1&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="配置使用">配置使用
&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>vscode：在settings.json中添加&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;terminal.integrated.fontFamily&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Cascadia Mono PL&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>windows terminal：在settings.json中添加&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;profiles&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;defaults&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;fontFace&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Cascadia Code PL&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> },
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> }
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>参考：&lt;/p>
